des:
Let the Bird Chirping sounds clear your mind and take you to a quiet place of reflection.

"Bird Chirping Sounds for Sleep and Relaxation” plays calming sound loops to help you fall asleep faster, sleep better, relax, meditate, or drown out distracting noises.

*** HOW TO USE ***

Enable Bird Chirping Sounds by clicking the "enable" button above, then say "Alexa, launch Bird Chirping".
By default, Alexa will play Bird Chirping Sounds. To pause ambient sound, say "Alexa, pause.” To resume it again, say "Alexa, resume."


*** PREMIUM MEMBERSHIP FEATURES ***

+ 100% increase in audio quality
+ Play different ambient sounds without any time limit 
+ Switch between ambient sounds using 'Next' and 'Previous' commands


*** REVIEWS AND FEEDBACK ***

Your reviews and feedback are important to us! If you love our skill, please consider showing your support by writing your valuable feedback.
